
Download:
https://www.apachelounge.com/download/ (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hUZso9TpEes)

Setup global environment variables:
update path "\Downloads\httpd-2.4.52-win64-VS16\Apache24\bin\"

Open cmd:
try to enter "ab"

Parameters:
-n requests     Number of requests to perform
-c concurrency  Number of multiple requests to make at a time (how many users will be sent the requests)

Notes:
url should be has "/" in the end of address 

Examples:
ab -n 10 -c 10 example.com/
ab -n 10 -c 10 example.com/ >log.txt (export the result into the log file)
